Title: Covariant - tensor method for quantum groups and applications I:
  $SU(2)_{q}$
Author: Stjepan Meljanac and Marijan Milekovic
Comments: 18 pages
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Quantum Algebra
Journal-ref: J.Phys. A26 (1993) 4595-4606
\\
  A covariant - tensor method for $SU(2)_{q}$ is described. This tensor method
is used to calculate q - deformed Clebsch - Gordan coefficients. The connection
with covariant oscillators and irreducible tensor operators is established.
This approach can be extended to other quantum groups.
